<br />\n太古一早已經奶共，當初自願將國泰股權交出媚共自保，繼續揾銀。反而怡和遷冊撤出香港。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/86420\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feastweek.my-magazine.me%2Fmain%2F86420&d=qWNbGjuqVnVY%2B89Bav9Y1BSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=dda4a143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://eastweek.my-magazine.me/main/86420</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新CEO 鄧生來自港機工程，一早紮根厦門，一定好識做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n去台灣，長榮/中華<br />\n<br />\n去日本， JAL ANA PEACH<br />\n<br />\n去歐洲 英航，三寶, virgin Air France lufthansa<br />\n<br />\n去澳洲 virgin qantas<br />\n<br />\n去美國 AA United<br />\n<br />\n去中國  冇計 國泰港龍"},{"pid":"4fb4b6cf61ac1f0530dc73959635a85457b833e4","tid":1481462,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:04:55.000Z","msg":"[香港淡奶] 屬於香港人嘅Timeline上線喇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481585\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481585</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6ca64c4305c5ec824b6edf764f6d56ef989d41d3","tid":1481462,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd8993821dd6c660bdd2420482f5ee314fb57e59","tid":1481462,"uid":207614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:06:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e6288c2e0e234acfe79f1db98f8b5284a567bdaa","tid":1481462,"uid":257398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"015d069a847f5f2223ab4044d7ee47aa705b4b27","tid":1481462,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"每個人都走唔甩<br />\n藍絲一樣波及<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T05:06:28.000Z","msg":"然後慢慢滲透各行各業，取代香港人位置"}]}